---
title: Beef Samosa-Style Pockets with Mango Chutney and Fresh Salad
description: Earthy and spice-filled Indian flavours come alive in this recipe! This meal is inspired by samosas, the popular Indian street snack. Ground beef is cooked with a fragrant spice mix, peas and potatoes, then gets tucked inside a pizza dough pocket and baked until steaming and crispy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pochettes-de-boeuf-facon-samoussas-dd7f6053.jpg
